      <title>皮博迪拟贷款 21 亿美元收购英美资源集团煤炭业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/peabody-lines-up-2-1-billion-loan-to-buy-anglo-s-coal-business</link>
